snippet.title: Olympic
snippet.description:
Welcome to the Olympic Channel! With new videos every day, we are the place where the Games never end!

From the best musical moments at the Olympic Games our Music Monday series to weekly compilations videos with highlights of the Olympics on Fridays and exclusive documentaries about the stories behind the glory, this is where you find everything about the biggest sporting event in the world.

snippet.title: Red Bull Surfing
snippet.description:
Welcome to the official Red Bull Surfing YouTube Channel! Watch weekly surf videos from across the world, with the likes of Jamie O'Brien, Jordy Smith, Kanoa Igarashi, Carissa Moore, Caroline Marks, Leo Fioravanti and more!

Connect with the best surfers out there and get to know their lifestyle, discover amazing surfing spots and get behind the scenes into the best live streams around, like Volcom Pipe Pro or Red Bull Cape Fear.

Let us take you behind the scenes and closer to the action, introducing you to the world of Red Bull Surfing. Remember to subscribe, like, share and let us know what you wanna see more of on our channel!

snippet.title: Cola Bros
snippet.description: We are the Colapinto Brothers! I Griffin, am 22 years old and my younger brother Crosby is 19 years old. We are both professional surfers Traveling the world. I am on the WSL World Championship Tour competing against the top 32 best surfers in the world. Crosby is on the Qualifying Series Tour working hard to reach our life long dream of being on the WCT together. On the side of the Contest, we are Goofy, weirdo kids who just wanna have fun! We will achieve our Dreams but we will make sure we have fun doing it. We also have lots of friends! We don't want everything to be just about us all the time, so we will be bringing in other funny characters that we think you'll get a kick out of! If you want to follow our journey, just subscribe to COLA BROS! Most of the Videos will be created by one of our best friends and creative wizard @Cameron_jonas

snippet.title: What If
snippet.description:
An epic exploration of possibilities. 

What If: These two simple words are the spark that has ignited countless theories, discoveries, and inventions. Most of what we know about ourselves and the universe is because someone, somewhere, at some time asked themselves “What if?” Join us on an imaginary adventure — grounded in scientific theory — through time, space and chance, as we ask what if some of the most fundamental aspects of our existence were different.

What If is a documentary web series that takes you on an epic journey through hypothetical worlds and possibilities, some in distant corners of the universe, others right here on Earth.

What If is produced by Underknown in Toronto, Canada (underknown.com) and made possible with the support of Ontario Creates (www.ontariocreates.ca)

Have a video idea? Suggest your what-if scenario over at whatifshow.com/suggest

snippet.title: Vans
snippet.description: Vans®, a VF Corporation (NYSE: VFC) brand, is the original action sports footwear, apparel and accessories brand. Vans authentic collections are sold globally in more than 75 countries through a network of subsidiaries, distributors and international offices. Vans also owns and operates more than 450 retail locations around the world. The Vans brand promotes the action sports lifestyle, youth culture and creative self-expression through the support of athletes, musicians and artists and through progressive events and platforms such as the Vans Triple Crown of Surfing®, the Vans U.S. Open of Surfing, Vans Pool Party, Vans Custom Culture, Vans Warped Tour®, and Vans’ cultural hub and international music venue, the House of Vans.
